Feature	URL
Login Page	http://127.0.0.1:8000/accounts/login/
Logout	http://127.0.0.1:8000/accounts/logout/
Admin Dashboard	http://127.0.0.1:8000/accounts/admin-dashboard/
Vendor Dashboard	http://127.0.0.1:8000/accounts/vendor-dashboard/
